{"tid":1048891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯「鯨魚監獄」慘不忍睹　 總統普京出手打救","createTime":"2019-03-06T01:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T00:08:20.000Z","uid":184679,"like":260,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"29eed7f791ac8a016ac1c1c4cd316def269d2511","tid":1048891,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/video-farm/thumbnail/24/24b231e53d4b241899ec6a2e480d3c1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fvideo-farm%2Fthumbnail%2F24%2F24b231e53d4b241899ec6a2e480d3c1b.jpg&h=a10092b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月，俄羅斯遠東港口納霍德卡（Nakhodka）的水域出現逾百隻鯨魚。這些鯨魚全被困在生活條件惡劣的設施之中，據報打算出售予中國的水族館。事件曝光後，總統普京親自發聲要求釋放鯨魚，遠在荷里活的影星也一同施壓。想知道事件的來龍去脈，請即點擊片段。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/302390/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF-%E9%AF%A8%E9%AD%9A%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84-%E6%85%98%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%8D%E7%9D%B9-%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC%E5%87%BA%E6%89%8B%E6%89%93%E6%95%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E8%25AA%25AA%2F302390%2F%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF-%25E9%25AF%25A8%25E9%25AD%259A%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%258D%2584-%25E6%2585%2598%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BF%258D%25E7%259D%25B9-%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E6%2599%25AE%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2595%2591&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=a312ac93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/302390/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF-%E9%AF%A8%E9%AD%9A%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84-%E6%85%98%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%8D%E7%9D%B9-%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC%E5%87%BA%E6%89%8B%E6%89%93%E6%95%91</a>"},{"pid":"bf0858cf7a33f655184ed8ade77245d9ab925a75","tid":1048891,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.g